(25917, 'Respatio 20 mg 20 f.c.tabs.', 'ريسباتيو 20مجم 20 قرص', '63', '94', 'Sildenafil', 'Marcyrl co. > pharma right group', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'مقوى للرجال', 'Tonic for men', '20 mg', 'Sildenafil is a phosphodiesterase-5 (PDE5) inhibitor that is predominantly employed for two primary indications:
