(3011, 'Controlepsy 50 mg 30 tab', 'كونترولبسي 50 مجم 30 قرص', '58.5', '78', 'Lamotrigine', 'Global napi pharmaceuticals', 'Tab', 'أقراص', 'علاج الصرع -- تقليل التشنجات الناتجة عن الصرع', 'Anti-epileptic.triazine', '50 mg', 'Lamotrigine is indicated as adjunctive therapy for the following seizure types in patients ≥2 years of age: partial seizures, primary generalized tonic-clonic seizures, and generalized seizures due to Lennox-Gastaut syndrome.[L9404]
